答标志 来指示是正常回应还是有某种错误发生。对正常回应,能源计量仪表回应相应的功能码。对异常回应相应的功能码但 。详细功能码见附录 。\",\n        \"bbox\": [\n            141,\n            255,\n            890,\n            309\n        ],\n        \"page_idx\": 5\n    },\n    {\n        \"type\": \"table\",\n        \"img_path\": \"images/d461300dfaff7a52f1bb7e154938b438cf568d0fa6cea1976bb2019df953907d.jpg\",\n        \"table_caption\": [],\n        \"table_footnote\": [],\n        \"table_body\": \"<table><tr><td rowspan=1 colspan=1>D7</td><td rowspan=1 colspan=1>D6</td><td rowspan=1 colspan=1>D5</td><td rowspan=1 colspan=1>D4</td><td rowspan=1 colspan=1>D3</td><td rowspan=1 colspan=1>D2</td><td rowspan=1 colspan=1>D1</td><td rowspan=1 colspan=1>D0</td></tr></table>\",\n        \"bbox\": [\n            163,\n            319,\n            835,\n            347\n        ],\n        \"page_idx\": 5\n    },\n    {\n        \"type\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": \"说明:\",\n        \"bbox\": [\n            137,\n            355,\n            183,\n            369\n        ],\n        \"page_idx\": 5\n    },\n    {\n        \"type\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": \"正常应答\",\n        \"bbox\": [\n            137,\n            372,\n            262,\n            386\n        ],\n        \"page_idx\": 5\n    },\n    {\n        \"type\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": \"异常应答\",\n        \"bbox\": [\n            137,\n            390,\n            262,\n            403\n        ],\n        \"page_idx\": 5\n    },\n    {\n        \"type\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": \"图2 功能域格式\",\n        \"bbox\": [\n            426,\n            416,\n            571,\n            431\n        ],\n        \"page_idx\": 5\n    },\n    {\n        \"type\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": \"424 数据域\",\n        \"text_level\": 2,\n        \"bbox\": [\n            107,\n            453,\n            230,\n            468\n        ],\n        \"page_idx\": 5\n    },\n    {\n        \"type\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": \"数据域指定了起始地址和要读写的寄存器数量等信息。\",\n        \"bbox\"